Watch on youtube: https://youtu.be/6IYkFwAuXQ0 Tags: 3dprint , material test , eryone , petg , According to the poll (link below), most of my viewers were curious for comparison of Eryone PETG and PETG-CF (version reinforced with the carbon fibers). Usually carbon fibers helps with printability, temperature resistance and stiffness along X,Y direction. But good news is, that here we have a good layer adhesion too (typical weak point of CF filaments).
